    "drop": false,
    "field": "finance",
    "role": "object",
    "bullets": [
      "Annual reports of more than 50 major banks worldwide over 2009 to 2023, used to build a text-based index of digital engagement at the bank-year level.",
      "Natural language processing quantifies digital engagement and large language models classify AI-related paragraphs by use case and implementation stage; no specific model is named and no validation is reported.",
      "Digital engagement is positively associated with profitability; fully operational AI in customer support, client profiling, and process optimization drives gains, while early-stage and regulatory or credit-scoring uses remain a cost."
    ],
